	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am not knowledgeable on caster classes, so feel free to correct me, but wouldn't a permanent damage shield of that size on a mage (in group or raid) be a bad thing?&nbsp;&nbsp;I am assuming (usually a bad idea) that any damage a mob receives from a damage shield further increases aggro.  If so, then if a mob breaks off and starts beating on the mage, then isn't it going to be that much harder to get it off before the mage is killed?<br>&nbsp;<br>Chapterhawk, 46th Paladin (Innoruuk Server, Spirit of the Moon)<br>&nbsp;&nbsp;I must really like dying in this game... 'cause I do it all the time.</td></tr>
