	   <tr><td colspan=2>You get hate from a DS only if you cast it while the mob is engaged with your target, this is because you're casting a beneficial spell on the target while it's on the mobs hate list. If the DS is on the player before they engage/aggro the mob, you don't generate any aggro from the DS.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Wed Mar 19 13:57:59 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Master Artulyn Starsummoner 62 Archmage of The Dedicated on Bertoxxulous<br>For the Light of a Candle to be Seen, It must be taken to a Dark Place -- UKLG</td></tr>
